<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="492" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1437,1411,1653]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">
The specimen here recognized as 
<typeStatus box="[539,637,1411,1437]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">holotype</typeStatus>
is a male bearing the labels: “ 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[988,1074,1411,1437]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pumilio">
<emphasis box="[988,1074,1411,1437]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">pumilio</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
m. in 
<collectingRegion box="[1151,1228,1411,1437]" country="Italy" name="Sicilia" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">Sicilia</collectingRegion>
”, “Schüppel.” and “ 
<typeStatus box="[161,268,1447,1473]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">Holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName authority="Dejean, 1829" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[311,808,1447,1473]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pumilio" subGenus="Ophonus">
<emphasis box="[311,643,1447,1473]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">Harpalus (Ophonus) pumilio</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." box="[653,808,1447,1473]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean, 1829</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. J. Serrano vidit.” 
<bibRefCitation author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." box="[1028,1192,1447,1473]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean (1829)</bibRefCitation>
wrote 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">
Je ne possède qu’un individu mâle de cette espèce; il m’a été envoyé par M. Schùppel, comme venant de 
<collectingRegion box="[1167,1229,1483,1509]" country="Italy" name="Sicilia" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">Sicile</collectingRegion>
</emphasis>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="492" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1437,1411,1653]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">
The species is currently known as 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Kataev &amp; Wrase" baseAuthorityYear="2017" box="[585,979,1519,1545]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Ophonus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pumilio" subGenus="Hesperophonus">
<emphasis box="[585,979,1519,1545]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">Ophonus (Hesperophonus) pumilio</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, as it shows the key characters of subgenus 
<taxonomicName authority="Antoine, 1959" authorityName="Antoine" authorityYear="1959" box="[197,539,1554,1581]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Ophonus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Hesperophonus">
<emphasis box="[197,372,1555,1581]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">Hesperophonus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Antoine, M." box="[376,539,1554,1581]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" pagination="315 - 465" refId="ref10238" refString="Antoine, M. (1959) Coleopteres Carabiques du Maroc. Troisieme partie. Memoires de la Societe des Sciences Naturelles et Physiques du Maroc, Nouvelle Serie, Zoologie, 6, 315 - 465." type="journal article" year="1959">Antoine, 1959</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. It has a small body size and a combination of dorsal colouration and leg characters that make it easily identifiable (
<bibRefCitation author="Fuente de la, J. M." box="[552,703,1591,1617]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" refId="ref10490" refString="Fuente de la, J. M. (1927) Tablas analiticas para la clasificacion de los coleopteros de la Peninsula Iberica. Adephaga: I Cicindelidae, II Carabidae. J. Bosch, Barcelona, 415 pp." type="book" year="1927">Fuente, 1927</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Antoine, M." box="[713,877,1590,1617]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" pagination="315 - 465" refId="ref10238" refString="Antoine, M. (1959) Coleopteres Carabiques du Maroc. Troisieme partie. Memoires de la Societe des Sciences Naturelles et Physiques du Maroc, Nouvelle Serie, Zoologie, 6, 315 - 465." type="journal article" year="1959">Antoine, 1959</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Sciaky, R." box="[888,1037,1591,1617]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" pagination="29 - 120" refId="ref12184" refString="Sciaky, R. (1987) Revisione delle specie paleartiche occidentali del genere Ophonus Dejean, 1821. Memoria della Societa Entomologica Italiana, 65, 29 - 120." type="journal article" year="1987">Sciaky, 1987</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1437,1411,1653]" box="[199,1329,1627,1653]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">
This species is distributed in the western Mediterranean (but not in 
<collectingCountry box="[954,1034,1627,1653]" name="France" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">France</collectingCountry>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Kataev, B. M. &amp; Wrase, D. W." box="[1045,1317,1627,1653]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" pagination="1810" refId="ref11718" refString="Kataev, B. M. &amp; Wrase, D. W. (2017 c) Subtribe Harpalina Bonelli, 1810. In: Lobl, I. &amp; Lobl, D. (Eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera. Vol. 1. Revised and Updated Edition. Brill, Leiden, pp. 515 - 562." type="book chapter" year="2017">Kataev &amp; Wrase, 2017c</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
